data.description:
Welcome to your new home in the west side of Massillon! This delightful split-level residence offers comfort, style, and ample space for you and your loved ones. Nestled in the Massillon City School District, this property presents an ideal opportunity for families seeking a cozy abode in a fantastic location.

Key Features: 
Bedrooms: 3
Bathrooms: 1.5
Living Area: Spacious and inviting 
Kitchen: Modern appliances, plenty of cabinet space
Outdoor Space: Fenced in yard, perfect for relaxation and recreation
Garage: Attached garage for convenient parking and extra storage

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The main level features a comfortable living area, perfect for gatherings with family and friends. The adjacent kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a cozy dining area, making meal preparation and entertaining a breeze. The dining room is right off the kitchen for easy access for all your family gatherings. 

Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, each offering comfort and privacy for every member of the household. A full bathroom conveniently serves the upper level, featuring updated fixtures and plenty of natural light.

Downstairs, a versatile lower level awaits, providing additional living space that can be tailored to suit your needs. Whether you envision a recreation room, or a cozy den, this flexible area offers endless possibilities. A convenient half bathroom and access to the attached garage complete the lower level.
The home is close to shopping, dining, parks, and recreational facilities, providing convenience and entertainment for the whole family. Easy access to major highways ensures effortless commutes to nearby cities and attractions. 

Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful split-level home your own. Schedule a showing today!

Roof just over 1 year old.  Kitchen flooring 1 year old. Selling contingent upon seller finding home of choice.
